title: Boone County Election Center
notes: Early voting will take place at the Boone County Election Center located at 414 W. Central Harrison, AR 72601. It is what Arkansas calls an off-site early voting site. Meaning not held at the county clerk's office. EV starts Mon Oct 24-Nov7. Voting hours are M-F 8 am- 6 pm except on November 7th then it is 8 am to 5 pm. On Saturdays, its 10- 4 pm.
